f armed popular militias.'' <PERSON> Carlos </PERSON> <PERSON> Caceres </PERSON>, the interior minister, said action was taken against the Communists `` to demonstrate the government's determination to have a peaceful transition to democracy. <PERSON> Sanfuentes </PERSON>, one of the defendants, said the government wants to `` prevent the <ORGANIZATION> Communist </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Party </ORGANIZATION>'s presence in the country's political life.''
