<HEAD>Rebel Leaders Say Willing to Meet With Sandinistas in Washington</HEAD>
<BYLINE>By CARLOS SANDI</BYLINE>
<BYLINE>Associated Press Writer</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>SAN JOSE, Costa Rica (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
